echo("Venezuela or the Bolivarian Republic of Venezuela is a country located in the north of South America.​ ​It is located in the northern hemisphere near the Equator landline. Its territory is composed of a compact land mass and a group of hundreds of archipelagos, islands or islets.​ ​It is located on the north coast of South America.​ ​It borders the North with the Caribbean Sea;​ ​to the south with the Republic of Brazil (with 2000 km of border);​ ​and to the east with the Republic of Guyana (743 km of border) and with the Atlantic Ocean;​ ​and to the west with the Republic of Colombia. It is located between the Caribbean Sea and the Cordillera.");